page_title: Azure OpenAI Service encryption of data at rest
page_description: Learn how Azure OpenAI encrypts your data when it's persisted to the cloud.
chunk_content: About Azure AI services encryptionAzure OpenAI is part of Azure AI services. Azure AI services data is encrypted and decrypted using FIPS 140-2 compliant 256-bit AES encryption. Encryption and decryption are transparent, meaning encryption and access are managed for you. Your data is secure by default and you don't need to modify your code or applications to take advantage of encryption.
